## Cross-ADR deps consumed here (per ADR-0055d §3):
##   0055a: TyArena, TyEntry, TyId, VarAllocator, insert, lookup, is_hashable, is_mutable_container,
##          subst_var, clone_into_arena, free_vars, record_from_pairs, FnTyEntry, RecordEntry
##   0055b: TypeError (all 25 variants), lib.cb re-export contract
##   0055c: Subst, subst_new, subst_apply, subst_extend, unify, finalize
